de.griefed.serverpackcreator.plugins.swinggui

Interface TabExtension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.pf4j.ExtensionPoint, PluginInformation

    public interface TabExtension
extends PluginInformation
    Plugin interface for plugins which are to be executed after the ServerPackCreator GUI have been initialized. This interface allows plugins to add additional JComponents as additional tabs.
